query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q1 tq1 s) NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('15.10',
'19.04',
'book-recommendation',
'complex-integration',
'diagonalization',
'display',
'ethernet',
'files',
'inverse-function',
'libreoffice',
'security',
'software-center',
'ssd',
'ubuntu-touch',
'windows-7')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 10
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Custodian',
'Editor',
'Popular Question',
'Scholar',
'Student',
'Tumbleweed') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
